p1034
tp1035
a(I0
VEvery act of vengeance generates another however, and soon the favela is a war-zone.
p1036
tp1037
a(I0
VWith its epic, three time period story of young men making their way, violently, in a life of crime, City Of God is like a Brazilian underclass GoodFellas.
p1038
tp1039
a(I0
