p4517
tp4518
aa(lp4519
(I0
V\u000aThe most enduring image The Hunger Games: Mockingjay - Part 1 offers is an eyeball-searing hell-scape of incinerated corpses, their ribs poking through blackened, immolated flesh.
p4520
tp4521
a(I0
