p4526
tp4527
a(I0
VAs the film opens, we pick up with Katniss (Jennifer Lawrence), furious that the rebel alliance led by President Coin (a frosty Julianne Moore) plotted to save her from the Hunger Games at the expense of her more expendable companions.
p4528
tp4529
a(I0
