p4536
tp4537
a(I0
VPlutarch Heavensbee (Philip Seymour Hoffman in his last role) attempts to media train Katniss into a serviceable mouth-piece for their cause, leading to comic scenes of desperation as he and his team realise quite what a dud screen presence she is when asked to play-act the revolution.
p4538
tp4539
a(I0
