p4542
tp4543
a(I0
VThere is a lot to get through in that third book, but much of it is internal and emotional, to do with how Katniss wrestles with everything that is demanded of her and with her feelings for Peeta, who is mostly restricted to brief onscreen glimpses as the Capitol cranks out its own propaganda making use of their most influential hostage.
p4544
tp4545
a(I0
